sequenceDiagram
    title Get ShortCourse Earnings

    participant Submit Learner Data
    participant Learner Data Outer
    participant Learning Inner Api
    participant Earnings Inner Api


    Submit Learner Data ->> Learner Data Outer: GetShortCourseEarnings (Get)

    Learner Data Outer ->> Learning Inner Api: GetForEarnings (Get)

    Learning Inner Api ->> Learner Data Outer : Ok 200 + learnings

    loop Parallel for each learning
        Learner Data Outer ->> Earnings Inner Api: GetFm99ShortCourseEarnings (Get) by learningKey
        Earnings Inner Api ->> Learner Data Outer : Ok 200 + earnings
    end

    Learner Data Outer ->> Submit Learner Data: Ok 200 + earnings for requested provider
